name: ENERGIA
description:
When I think of what I do, I think of this energy that lives in me. I've never observed it more than now, and I realize that it's externalized with every step that I take. In symbols, in tattoos, in expression... this inflection in the manifestation of the things I do, have to do with what lives in me and many other factors that altered my expressive language. In this and my previous work: RUIDO. I try to bring these values to life. And I'm curious to know what this tito is going to be. 

Twitter: @tit0puyo

Agust 1-3  2021.
